,Recommended,283100,10024513,"Posted: 4 May, 2014",all,Linkthehobo,"Surprisingly Fun with some great mechanics. I was put off by the seemingly ""OP"" Early Access pack weapons until I realized that nearly EVERY weapon in the game will destroy a 50hp player in no time. The DPS on weapons matters little in PVP, but is a great help in farming PvE or attempting to take down a base shield(Has not yet been done with the 2000 shields !). The communities in the game are slowly growing, and the danger of losing your hard work is real, but intelligence and some good design sense will allow any player to create a near unbreakable fortress. Although as more and more players acquire top tier weapons shields will likely fall, meaning you will need to band together and push deep into the heart of uncharted sectors to construct your hideaways and bases.Worth the price to purchase Early Access IMO. Group play is hilarious, high energy and enjoyable. Periods of downtime and large maps mean you might not see another player or you may see five, it is all going to come down to visibility on Steam for this title, and it does have the potential to be a gem in my opinion.This game is for HARDCORE PvP players and players who enjoy building and PvE Alien Swarm esque shooters. I enjoy the fact that nobody is safe, while also being able to protect yourself quite well. Groups of 10+ have been unable to breech my shields, so I've lost only a single base so far. Check out the Citizen Pack Option and get keys to your friends while you can! The packs are likely to be removed from Steam within a week.Hope to see you all ingame soon!"
